---
// "Why McCauley" section with animations
---

<section class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-warm-white section-divider">
  <div class="w-full px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24">
    <div class="max-w-5xl">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-8 reveal-up">
        Why McCauley
      </h2>
      <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-gray-mid leading-relaxed reveal-up" style="transition-delay: 0.2s">
        Your home is changing. Do not just find a contractor — find a partner. 
        We help you move forward with clarity, confidence, and craftsmen who have 
        been doing this since 1978.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-cream overflow-hidden">
  <div class="w-full px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="max-w-xl">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-8 reveal-left">
          This is not just about remodeling.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-mid leading-relaxed reveal-left" style="transition-delay: 0.2s">
          It is about how you live. It is about making your space work for your family. 
          You are not just looking for cabinets and countertops. You are looking for a 
          home that fits who you have become. That is what we help you build.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Accent image -->
      <div class="reveal-right img-zoom rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <img 
          src="/images/accent-transformation.png" 
          alt="Home transformation" 
          class="w-full"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
